My awp_office map, my main objective was to stay as close os possible to office origionally.  Its a little on the big side, but as players spawn with deagles, nades and armour, it makes it a little more than your average awp map.

I will be adapting this into a cs map before the new years, completed this in under 4 days too.  May update this sometime to include stuff I wanted to but ran out of time for, such as snow, HDR and radar.
